name: Gela Yeens (V)
Lore: 'Bad-tempered smuggler. Makes a few credits more helping Jabba collect debts. Highly regarded for his uncanny anticipation in battle. Searching for Debnoli.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. Opponent may not target Gela Yeens (or a starship he pilots) with weapons. While in battle with Jabba, opponent''s characters at same site are power and forfeit -2.',
